{"tid":633903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打幫幫手 我隻腳趾好耐未好 （內有圖）","createTime":"2018-04-18T16:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T06:51:26.000Z","uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60765ab260307ffcc65a2437aaf8491649feedea","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"我應該睇咩科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇過 一個全科 佢就打針同消炎藥<br />\n但衣家塊甲係邊邊生緊出黎<br />\n搞到 兩舊肉分分開埋<br />\n點算好<br />\n核突左少少 唔好意思<br />\n成半年喇😭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/005603_2cc0ac7c488a0681a4aba3f483da2882.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F005603_2cc0ac7c488a0681a4aba3f483da2882.png&h=7f5c2bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/005605_0c53f0e70573e21014dd0ed0574cee3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F005605_0c53f0e70573e21014dd0ed0574cee3b.png&h=5d55e634&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73edbf23c6b8e097660d8d00889b42ffff865c8a","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711dd290626db32c0077dfb5fd3b616fc512b44b","tid":633903,"uid":745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"生活有影響？"},{"pid":"08f7b05762b979b796ff7b5371b3b428ed2b9532","tid":633903,"uid":33635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"你應該係嵌甲？<br />\n一係就睇醫生叫佢幫你整返出嚟<br />\n一係就自由忍痛土炮揾嘢撩返條甲出嚟剪咗佢<br />\n<br />\n以後剪腳甲唔好再剪得咁入<br />\n我細個成日都係咁樣<br />\n我忍痛忍到眼水都咇埋咁樣撩返佢出嚟剪<br />\n剪完個下好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b532113b947d783ba15ad579a5a7df144e0f8c57","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"