0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02ff3db3cfbe4c06a35d39e891e2efcf67848e06","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9c9c9d5b5d5705c6117df53c9873c2f15237659","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"剪到盡入，用陰力Hold住指甲鉗meet出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"首先你要用尖嘴指甲鉗，將個鉗嘴塞到盡量靠近邊邊嘅位置再剪，然後再meet佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔明就Quote多次，我畫圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再利申，呢個方法已經救咗唔少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ced581b05ca9eb1f1469a67962dd2bd4ff5bd7","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg&h=622b09c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24f2845138cd6fc1b4baa378aa79657750478c7c","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/135923_edee01b46e62f7af92a5eb34c008dc06.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F135923_edee01b46e62f7af92a5eb34c008dc06.jpeg&h=68d8285f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尖嘴指甲鉗如圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剪完記得消毒隻腳，同埋如果有含濃的話一定要吱哂出黎，頭兩日盡量就保持通風啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1ef253563ad9057ce23165ae34cca6c4a1a74","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ced581b05ca9eb1f1469a67962dd2bd4ff5bd7","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg&h=622b09c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有（龍）要吉穿佢 吱出黎？"},{"pid":"b53962f89da8a95f13ba25a622dd4353dea49671","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ca1ef253563ad9057ce23165ae34cca6c4a1a74","tid":633903,"uid":95534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ced581b05ca9eb1f1469a67962dd2bd4ff5bd7","tid":633903,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F135754_f23e7ebba08a037cf60b30cbf804d526.jpeg&h=622b09c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有（龍）要吉穿佢 吱出黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-